      <title>阿联酋提高减产执行率，OPEC 12 月产量下降</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/opec-output-dips-in-december-as-uae-improves-delivery-of-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于阿联酋加大减产力度以提振全球石油市场，石油输出国组织 (OPEC) 的原油产量上个月出现下降。]]></description>
